Many patents describe non-explosive demolition agents containing [[CaO]], [[Silicon dioxide|SiO<sub>2</sub>]] and/or [[cement]].<ref>http://www.baustoffchemie.de/en/db/non-explosive-demolition-agent-patents/</ref>
